          <h3 class="blue-title">What is EV?</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <h1><i class="fa fa-smile-o fa-3x"></i></h1>
          <p>EV stands for Expected Value. Simply put when you blindly bet on an outcome, that bet must fall into one of the 3 categories: negative EV (-EV), breakeven EV (=), and positive EV (+EV). Here at Puntsquad we aim only to offer +EV tips, where the price offered is better than the likelihood of the outcome occurring, and hence we expect to make money and come out ahead in the long run.  </p>
        </div>
      </div>
